data.description: Welcome to this immaculate, turnkey traditional home, perfectly situated in the highly desirable Wyngate subdivision and within the sought-after Bascomb Elementary School district. This residence effortlessly combines timeless style with practical functionality, offering an exquisite living experience. Upon arrival, the home's pristine exterior with recent updates immediately catches your eye, enhancing its overall appeal. Step inside and be welcomed by the natural hardwood floors that flow seamlessly into a dining area adjacent to a versatile flex space, ready to adapt to your preferences, whether it be a den, office, or playroom. Beyond lies a sun-drenched two-story gathering room, complete with a cozy gas fireplace, creating an inviting atmosphere that opens up to the well-appointed kitchen. The kitchen is a haven for culinary enthusiasts, featuring granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, abundant counter space, and ample storage – a rare and sought-after combination. Journey upstairs to discover three secondary bedrooms that share a tastefully designed bathroom, as well as the expansive owner's suite. The en-suite bathroom leaves nothing to be desired, boasting a double vanity, a luxurious soaking tub, a spacious walk-in shower, and an abundance of natural light. Located in the heart of Towne Lake, you'll enjoy easy access to Woodstock's premier shopping and dining destinations, Lake Allatoona for outdoor recreation, and the I-575 express lane for seamless commuting. This home is the epitome of perfection – seize the opportunity to make it your own.
